commits.content:
{
  "name": "electron-app",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "An Electron application with React and TypeScript",
  "main": "./out/main/index.js",
  "author": "qirong77",
  "homepage": "https://www.electronjs.org",
  "scripts": {
    "format": "prettier --write .",
    "lint": "eslint . --ext .js,.jsx,.cjs,.mjs,.ts,.tsx,.cts,.mts --fix",
    "typecheck:node": "tsc --noEmit -p tsconfig.node.json --composite false",
    "typecheck:web": "tsc --noEmit -p tsconfig.web.json --composite false",
    "typecheck": "npm run typecheck:node && npm run typecheck:web",
    "start": "electron-vite preview",
    "dev": "electron-vite dev",
    "build": "npm run typecheck && electron-vite build",
    "postinstall": "electron-builder install-app-deps",
    "build:win": "npm run build && electron-builder --win --config",
    "build:mac": "electron-vite build && electron-builder --mac --config",
    "build:linux": "electron-vite build && electron-builder --linux --config"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@electron-toolkit/preload": "^1.0.2",
    "@electron-toolkit/utils": "^1.0.2",
    "@milkdown/plugin-clipboard": "^6.4.1",
    "@milkdown/plugin-indent": "^6.5.0",
    "@milkdown/preset-gfm": "^6.5.0",
    "electron-updater": "^4.6.5"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@electron-toolkit/tsconfig": "^1.0.1",
    "@material-design-icons/font": "^0.12.1",
    "@milkdown/core": "^6.4.1",
    "@milkdown/plugin-history": "^6.4.1",
    "@milkdown/plugin-listener": "^6.4.1",
    "@milkdown/plugin-menu": "^6.4.1",
    "@milkdown/plugin-prism": "^6.4.2",
    "@milkdown/preset-commonmark": "^6.4.2",
    "@milkdown/react": "^6.4.1",
    "@milkdown/theme-nord": "^6.4.1",
    "@types/node": "16.11.22",
    "@types/react": "18.0.21",
    "@types/react-dom": "18.0.6",
    "@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin": "^5.39.0",
    "@typescript-eslint/parser": "^5.39.0",
    "@vitejs/plugin-react": "^2.1.0",
    "electron": "^20.3.2",
    "electron-builder": "^22.14.13",
    "electron-notarize": "^1.2.1",
    "electron-vite": "^1.0.10",
    "eslint": "^8.24.0",
    "eslint-config-prettier": "^8.5.0",
    "eslint-plugin-prettier": "^4.2.1",
    "eslint-plugin-react": "^7.31.8",
    "katex": "^0.16.2",
    "prettier": "^2.7.1",
    "prism-themes": "^1.9.0",
    "react": "^18.2.0",
    "react-dom": "^18.2.0",
    "sass": "^1.55.0",
    "typescript": "^4.7.4",
    "vite": "^3.1.6"
  }
}
